{"name":"Lady Sinister","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"","alignment":"Chaotic Neutral","hitDice":"5","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"15","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"100","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"12","conPoints":"10","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"18","chaPoints":"20","blindsight":"60","blind":true,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"8","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"True Demonic Form","desc":"Upon reaching 1/4th of her total hit points or Lord Sinister reaching 1/4th of his total hit points, Lady Sinister transforms into her final demonic form, a large incorporeal shadow of herself, pushing all players away from her for 60ft and gaining Huge size. Every DC check players make against her for the rest of combat now has a DC of 20, all her attacks gain 30ft in range and her hit points cannot drop below 1 unless Lady Sinister's hit-points are also 1."},{"name":"Shapechanger.","desc":"Lady Sinister can use her action to polymorph into a Small or Medium humanoid, or back into her original form, maintaining the same stats regardless of her form."},{"name":"Telepathic Bond","desc":"Lady Sinister can telepathically communicate with any creature she has charmed."},{"name":"Invisibility","desc":"If Lady Sinister has not taken any damage on the last turn (or if this is the beginning of combat), she hides in the shadows, becoming invisible to any player who is not within 10 ft of her."}],"actions":[{"name":"Whip of Eternal Agony","desc":"Lady Sinister attacks a player with an ethereal whip she materialises from her hands. A creature attacked by the whip must make a DC 15 Strength check or find themselves grappled. Once a whip has grappled a player, Lady Sinister can let go of it and it will remain grappled unless the player escapes. While a player is grappled by the whip, they have disadvantage in DC rolls and take 1d6 radiant damage per turn.\n\nMelee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 30 ft., one target. Hit: 6 (1d6 + 3) radiant damage"},{"name":"Restrains of the Soul","desc":"Lady Sinister plunges her ethereal claws into a creature, gripping their heart tightly. A creature must make a DC 15 wisdom saving throw otherwise, they remain grappled and paralysed by Lady Sinister. If a creature remains paralysed for at least 3 turns this way, they take 10d10 Radiant damage. Upon completion, this action cannot be done for another 3 turns.\n\nIf a creature does not have a heart, this spell has no effect."},{"name":"Look into my eyes","desc":"Lady Sinister picks a creature within sight and forms a telepathic bond with them. On the first turn of this spell, a creature must make a DC 15 Wisdom saving throw, or be blinded until the next combat, only being able to see her eyes in the darkness. On the next turn if they fail another DC 15 Wisdom check, the creature becomes charmed and loses their blindness. Any creature which succeeds a roll breaks free of the telepathic bond and regains their sight. If Lady Sinister already has a bond with another creature, the newly targeted creature is charmed and the effects run out on the previous one."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Spectral Dash","desc":"Lady Sinister dashes 30ft towards any direction, dealing 1d10 radiant damage to any creature standing in her path."},{"name":"Draining Kiss","desc":"Lady Sinister picks any charmed or willing creature within 5ft of her and kisses it. A creature kissed this way must make a DC 15 Constitution save. If it fails its maximum hit points are decreased by 5d10 until that creature finishes a long rest. If it succeeds, the effect still passes with 2d10 instead."},{"name":"Maddening Whispers","desc":"Lady Sinister picks any charmed creature within sight and unleashes an onslaught of maddening whispers through her telepathic bond with them. A creature that can hear the whispers must make a DC 15 Wisdom check. Upon failure, the creature is feared and takes 1d4 psychic damage for every turn it remains feared."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"animal Handling","stat":"wis"},{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"performance","stat":"cha"},{"name":"persuasion","stat":"cha"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"necrotic","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"slashing","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"blinded"}],"languages":[{"name":"Abyssal","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Undercommon","speaks":t